
Muchidzidzo che[[Kupimanzvimbo]], [[zhumwi]] (Prism) chiumbwa chine nzenda nhatu (3-dimensional); icho chiumbwa chinotaridzika kunge chiumbwa chine nzenda mbiri chakatatamurwa zvichitevedza kunoenda mutwi unobva pahwaro. (Appears like a 2-dimensional shape that has been translated along a line perpendicular to the base, so that all parallel cross-sections have the same shape) 

Somuenzaniso, [[zhumwi regonyanhatu]] (triangular prism) rine uso huviri hwakati [[sambamba]]; [[mucheko]] yose yakati sambamba nemiviri yarehwa pamusoro inenge ine chiumbwa che[[gonyanhatu]] zvakare.
